mixin valid-label(form, name, label, value)
  label
    = label
    span(ng-show="needFix && "+form+"."+name+".$invalid")
      i.glyphicon.glyphicon-exclamation-sign.text-danger
      .text-danger(ng-show=form+"."+name+".$error.required") 此欄位爲必填
      .text-danger(ng-show="!"+form+"."+name+".$error.required")
        | 這不是正確的
        = value
    .text-success(ng-show="!"+form+"."+name+".$invalid")
      i.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok-sign

